	<p id="_8de0d937-61fd-4e69-833f-9aaac5dbe805">Communicating recommendations to the JCTLM Secretariat for listing reference measurement services of laboratories accredited (according to ISO/IEC 17025 and ISO 15195) is the responsibility of the DB WG vice-chair(s).</p>
