	<p id="_32d89539-3387-4b9c-b2bf-4924d1561cec">Reference Measurement Services Nomination Form available at: <link target="https://www.bipm.org/utils/common/pdf/JCTLM/DBWG-P-02B-F-01.xls"/></p></clause></clause>
