	<p id="_76f4c3d8-48cd-4048-92b8-02bc6112db6c">If the procedure implemented in the laboratory to deliver the reference measurement service differs from the Reference Method listed in the JCTLM database, but uses the same basic principle of measurement, and has been fully validated, the laboratory must provide the validation report of the modified method for its assessment by the experts of the review teams and its publication in the database if approved by JCTLM</p>
