	<clause id="_29" obligation="normative"><p id="_20076fca-d412-4d60-b8f0-c84e253450c4">Submitting nomination forms for consideration by the DB WG:</p>
	<clause id="_30" obligation="normative">
	
	<p id="_ef215951-f5f5-43a1-88fa-49470a2500ca">The JCTLM Secretariat preliminary reviews submitted nominations for completeness within six weeks of their receipt in consultation with the DB WG Chair and vice-chair(s).</p>
