	<clause id="_42" obligation="normative"><p id="_c25d83d6-88d1-486a-b042-5885aa6a8c46">The secretariat compiles all review forms and recommendations and forwards these to the DB WG vice-Chair(s) for verification. Queries raised by the vice-Chair(s) are returned to the Review Team Leader and the JCTLM Secretariat. Answers to queries and the review teams’ recommendations and review forms are returned to the JCTLM Secretariat.</p>
	<clause id="_43" obligation="normative">
	
	<p id="_a1ffaf85-5fa4-4a40-8f13-721d64160e7d">The DB WG reviews at its annual meeting the recommendations from the review teams prior formal approval by the JCTLM Executive. (See DB WG P-05)</p>
	</clause>
